Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.42,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Kanjiru yokan ni shoot I love fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:56.76,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Tsubasa ni ishi o mi o yudanete
