Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:05.39,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Isso uso demo ii kara seigi o tsuranuku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:09.52,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Saiko no shiawase ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:17.28,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Tada sore dake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:33.53,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Berdoa tak akan menghasilkan apapun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:35.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Aku tahu itu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:38.28,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Meski rasa takut kehilangan menghalangi kita,
