Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Tak melihat, tak peduli...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:47.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Mereka yang bahkan tak memberi kebebasan atau pun cinta,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:49.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}para malaikat dari langit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Firasatku berbicara, ya, aku suka takdir!
