Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:03:01.68,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Tanpa lelah ku terus hidup di dunia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:05.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Jadilah pembela kebenaran meski hanya sandiwara.
